room_title: Escape room "Alpha Lab" by Escape Brigade in Chicago
room_address: 2720 South River Road Ste 12 Des Plaines, IL 60018
room_description: Little did you know, when you were busy doing your regular office job, your employer was working on an evil plan which will endanger millions of lives! The police are desperately looking for evidence. You have to help them find it! Break into the lab your boss runs, eliminate the threat and escape before it's too late!
